data.description: Adorable property in East Dallas! This home has three beds, two baths with newer windows, beautiful original hardwood floors, and high ceilings throughout. This will make an excellent home for first time homebuyers! It would also be a wonderful investment opportunity or a great place for those wanting to downsize. The master has double closets, making for ample closet space. This property has lots of character and a versatile floor plan with two separate living-dining areas so the possibilities are endless! The open concept kitchen with gas stove has brand new ceramic tile and plenty of cabinetry! Large back patio with nicely landscaped yard has a high yielding fig bearing fruit tree that the new owners are sure to enjoy. Come view today! :)
